    "description": "Nexus Malls, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Sales Manager for our Pune operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Nexus Malls:\nNexus Malls is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nexus Malls!",
